cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM

This paper deals with image processing and computer vision, specifically the detection and localization of contours in images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of Gestaltism in edge grouping, which falls under the category of graphics (cs.GR). The torque operator is a mid-level image operator, which involves some level of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper discusses the application of the torque operator in object recognition, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
